  "body": "Shutting down the HTTP server currently breaks off all current requests. This can create a race condition with RPC `stop` command, where the calling process never receives confirmation.\n\nThis change removes the listening sockets on shutdown so that no new requests can come in, but no longer breaks off requests in progress.\n\nMeant to fix #6717.\n",
